---
title: Greek Chicken Tzatziki Bowls with Chicken Thighs, Yellow Rice & Pitas
description: The flavors of a Greek souvlaki platter are front and center in this abundant one-bowl meal. Oregano and garlic-seasoned chicken is served over golden turmeric rice, with warm pita triangles and lemon wedges on the side. A creamy, lemony cucumber-dill tzatziki-style yogurt sauce rounds out this savory spread.
